# Enterprise-Grade Monitoring with Prometheus & Grafana

This project demonstrates how to monitor a Python web app deployed on Kubernetes using Prometheus and Grafana.

## What it does
- Deploys a simple Python app using Flask.
- Installs Prometheus to collect metrics.
- Installs Grafana to visualize metrics from Prometheus.

## How to run

1. Deploy the Python app:
```bash
kubectl apply -f k8s
kubectl apply -f monitoring
